@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dnqnal(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (tmp / wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.08)))
    v1 = wp.abs((v2 + (v2 + 0.66 * v0 + 0.98)))
    tmp = wp.sin((0.16 + wp.abs(v0 + 0.17)))
    v0 = 0.09
    tmp = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.68 + v2 + 0.37) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.28)))
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin((0.25 + wp.exp(tmp + 0.82)))
    data[tid] = v0
